.TH devin-cloud-drs-build-logs 1  "build-logs " 
.SH NAME
devin\-cloud\-drs\-build\-logs \- Fetch the log stream for a build job
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBdevin cloud drs build\-logs\fR <\fB\-\-build\-job\-id\fR> [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Fetch the log stream for a build job
.PP
Outputs NDJSON log lines from the snapshot builder. Useful for diagnosing `partial` or `failed` builds.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-\-build\-job\-id\fR \fI<BUILD_JOB_ID>\fR
Build job ID to fetch logs for
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help (see a summary with \*(Aq\-h\*(Aq)
